Classes in suncertify.db used by suncertify.api
DuplicateKeyException
          Exception signalizes an attempt to store in the database a row with already existing key .
RecordNotFoundException
          Exception signalizes that the requested row either does not exist or is marked as deleted.
SecurityException
          Exception signalizes an attempt to modify a row or release a lock by client who either did not obtain a lock or is using wrong lock cookie.
